Structure:


	App
│   ├── controllers:They are used for processing requests and generating response.
│   ├── models:Models include all the logic required to interact with the database. 		It is actually used for data representation.
│   └── views:It constitutes all the views related to the web application. These 			views are displayed to the end users with the help of controllers.
└──Config
	└──router:The router component allows to define routes that are mapped to the 		controllers or handlers that should receive the request. A router parses a 		URI as per the information received.
|
└── public
    ├── css
    ├── img
    ├── index.php
    └── js
│
│
│
│
│
│